  conference-url = {\url{http://www.hotmobile.org/2023/}},
  abstract = {We demonstrate how to leverage Apple's Find\,My protocol, most
    well known as the underlying protocol of the AirTag, for arbitrary
      data-muling and location services. This provides a new ``infrastructure-free''
